00:21:51.990 --> 00:21:53.670
Señor Chengyun de la montaña Yaoguang, Ming Xin,

00:21:53.710 --> 00:21:55.710
Usé este espejo para burlarme de Jixing Abyss,

00:21:55.880 --> 00:21:56.950
